● During any spin, the Fortune Panda Feature may be  randomly triggered while the reels are spinning.
● During the Fortune panda Feature, a symbol is  randomly chosen( exluding Wild symbol) , and the  reels will consist only the randomly chosen symbol, Wild symbol or blank space.

● After all reels stop spinning, if there is 1 or more  additional symbol(either a randomly chosen symbol  or a Wild symbol) appearing on the reels, all reels will  respin again with the previously appeared symbols  staying in their positions.
● After all reels stop spinning, if there is no more  additional symbol (either a randomly chosen symbol  or a Wild symbol) appearing on the reels, the  Fortune Panda feature ends and wins are paid.
● When all symbol in the reels are involved in a win，the win will be multiplied by x10.
● Stand a chance to win up to 2500x of the total bet  amount.
● Only the highest win per bet line is paid.
● Bet lines win if the winning symbols are in succession  from the leftmost reel to the right.
